Why give? What are the benefits?

The main benefit of consistently giving away your money is that it develops a spirit of generosity in your soul. Over time, youâ€™ll be able to earn more money by being more generous. You will attract opportunities and multiply your inflows.

How much to give? What % of your inflows should you give?

At least 10% of your budget, up to 20%. 10% will provide you with a sense of never having to worry about money again, and 20% will maximize your wealth building potential.

